V-Clip Library Distribution, version 1.0

Contents:

Makefile	Makefile for all targets
Readme		this file
doc		documentation
examples	example programs that don't require Inventor
include		header files for V-Clip
iv_examples	example programs that require Inventor
lib		where the V-Clip library is put
ptrees		sample PolyTree files
src		source code for V-Clip


Follow the two steps listed in the Makefile, and then do a make in
this directory to build the V-Clip library(s) and example programs.
Readme files in the various directories give more information.  This
distribution was developed using SGI's 7.1 C++ compiler for IRIX 6.2.

